description: Iris has to take out Shuji Wai Hong Li the leader of the Academy but for this she needs help. Lily and some other Executive Assistants who are out for revenge are willing to help Iris. While Lily and her team distract the guards Iris is able to intrude into the Academy. The students are forced to stop Lily but she persuades them to fight alongside her team to take down the evil leader of the Academy. Iris finally finds Shuji who is protected by two more Executive Assistants but are no match for Iris. Eventually it´s only the two left...
name: Lies, Lies, Lies

description:
Excalibur is back, just the way you like them! From the ashes of House of M a new Excalibur team is formed to combat the aftereffects of this cataclysmic event! Witness the birth of Captain Britain's new team forming, as a sinister force already tries to tear them apart! Starring Dazzler, Juggernaut, Nocturne and Pete Wisdom!! Guest-starring the Uncanny X-Men! Plus: Still reeling from M-Day, New Excalibur is brought together to become Europe's premier super team. Not everyone is pleased. Guest starring Lionheart (from the pages of AVENGERS)!    
 
Reprints New Excalibur #1-7.
name: Volume 1

description: Kazuha contends with the rivalry between the Sugimoto brothers. Maki, the one she's in love with, resents Saki, the brother who teaches at Kazuha's school—and the feeling may be mutual. Now we'll learn how their mother blamed Maki for all of their family misfortunes and how a mysterious woman became involved in this family feud.Will all of this information affect Kazuha's feelings toward Maki?
name: Volume 9

volume.name: I Hate You More than Anyone

description: Homer decides it's time to take his government rebate and turn in his old clunker for a new eco-friendly car. But he soon learns that 'eco-friendly' does not necessarily mean 'more convenient' or 'new and improved' and he tries to get his old sedan back. However, he's going to have to save his 'old bucket of bolts' before it really turns into an old bucket of bolts.
name: Pardon My Clunker; Baby, Yoy CAn Drive My Hearse

description: Having endured a fierce battle with the Spider Ninjas last issue, Sonic and his friends must now face Bat Ninjas! While ambushes threaten around every corner, the intrepid heroes proceed on their journey to the temple under the firm resolves of Sally and Monkey Khan. Are these deadly skirmishes any match for the political chess games and machinations of war that lurk beneath the surface? The big picture gets even bigger in this issue that ties into this month's SONIC THE HEDGEHOG #211.
name: Journey to the East, Part Two: High Price For Rich Nights

description: Before the existence of pop-culture sharpshooter MAD MAGAZINE there was the original MAD — as in, Tales Calculated to Drive You MAD! Twenty-three comic book issues that threw the rule-book out the window and redefined comedy and satire for generations to come. It's visionary humor in a jugular vein, presented in a handsome hardcover format. Here is where it all began.
name: Volume 1

description: This second volume collecting the early issues of MAD COMICS features classic material from issues #7-12, including "Shermlock Sholmes," "Dragged Net," and "Little Orphan Melvin"!
name: Volume 2

description:
The biggest cowboy star of the silent movie era, and one of the greatest Western film stars ever returns in this superb package of classic reprints of his Fawcett Comics series from the Golden Age of comics that appeared in that companies’ Master Comics title. Stories include “Bushwhacked”, “The Strong Box Mystery”, “The Shadows Of The Grave” and “The Justice Killer”. All stories are illustrated by the top art team of Carl Pfeufer and John Jordan. Color photo front, and black and white insides and back covers, interiors are color and black and white with graytones. 44 pages, standard comic book format, printed in 1988.

"Special limited edition"

A thrilling collection of up-and-coming talent tackles Superman and the heroes of Metropolis! Packed with guest stars galore including Bizarro, Lois Lane and many more, these timeless tales of The Man of Steel are destined to thrill!
name: Cold; Patience-Centered Care; Got Bugs?; Why Metropolis?; Superman Is My Co-Pilot; Five Minutes; On Break

description: Having beaten off the pirate attack, Mister No, Duval and his men enter the Kalahari desert to deliver their load. They arrive at the headquarters of Southern Diamonds Company, which however, is attacked by outlaws led by the Martin brothers!
name: Kalahari!

description: After arriving in Arusha, in Tanganika, near the border of Kenya, thanks to a lift from the amicable private pilot Billy MacKinley, Mister No heads towards Nairobi, where his friend Jimmy Collins lives. But he sees Tony Steele, a professional hunter who has fun persecuting animals and….
name: Nairobi Autostop

description: In prison as a result of a fight with the white hunter, Mister No gets out thanks to the ethologist Konrad, who pays the bail, on the condition that Jerry accepts to be the pilot for him and his daughter Ketty, who plan to explore the Serengeti Park. Konrad asks the Masai to regulate the grazing of the animals, but he meets ferocious opposition from Kiamba, the young leader of the Moran warriors…
name: I Razziatori della Savana

description: Giving in to Ketty’s persistent requests, Mister No joins an expedition against the poachers and discovers that their leader is Kiamba, the Moran warrior leader. Kiamba then kills the wise man Najj, accusing Mister No of his death and inciting the Masai to revolt!
name: La Rivolta dei Masai

description: Mister No and Ketty manage with difficulty to escape from Bauer’s farm, which is besieged by the Masai. During their flight, they find old Najj, the Masai “laibon”. He is still alive, and reveals to them that Kiamba attempted to kill him. Thanks to him, there is a chance of restoring peace to the region…
name: L'Ultima Pallottola

description: Kenya is in flames! Guerrilla warfare is raging between the English Colonial troops and the proud Mau-Mau. And war often brings unjustified violence: even the amicable Kunz, a Swiss friend of Mister No, is killed…
name: Mau-Mau

description: Finally Mister No meets Jimmy Collins, who has been hardened by the guerrilla warfare. Now Jimmy leads a division of Moran, the Masai warriors that are traditionally enemies of the Kikuyu rebels, and he has massacred many of the resistance: they call him Kikuyu killer! For this reason the Mau-Mau have decided to kidnap his son Tommy!
name: Tempesta sul Kenya

description: Pretending to be an arms trader, Mister No manages to enter the rebel camp where little Tommy is to be found. He watches the frightening, bloody Mau-Mau rite and, when the warriors are about to sacrifice Tommy, he has to intervene!
name: Lo Stregone Kikuyu

description: An unmotivated massacre. The end of a friendship. A hard beating-up. Mister No’s farewell to Kenya is bitter. Jimmy Collins is by now a bloodthirsty brute, a shadow of the friend Jerry remembered. Fortunately, the pilot is able to save Jimmy’s son Tommy: he is the hope for a better Kenya. But a great danger is awaiting Mister No on the way to the airport…
name: Furore!

description: Garrison, an archaeologist Mister No met in South America, hires him to save his daughter, who is being kept in confinement by a lovesick Arab, but in actual fact Garrison wants to bombard a dam in the Sudan from the plane! Although Garrison eventually decides not to carry out this plan, once they have landed he and Jerry are seized by mysterious men. And the archaeologist is tortured to death!
name: La Diga nel Deserto

description: The fanatical sect of El Azif, that wants to unite the all Arab peoples by bringing them back into the fold of the “ancient religion”, is searching for a long-lost object. An object that the expedition headed by Linda Garrison, Professor Garrison’s daughter, is perhaps about to bring to light…
name: Il Faraone Dimenticato

description: Mister No sets off into the intricate maze dedicated to the pharaoh Ekhnaton. Through mysterious doors, monstrous images flood his mind, and, after passing through various initiation ordeals, he meets a centuries-old being …
name: Labirinto Infernale

description: Crime boss had tried to implicate Natasha as a drug peddler by implanting drugs in Natasha's apartment. But the boy who had planted the drugs was under police custody and recuperating in a hospital. Barco knew that it was a matter of time before his devious plan shall be exposed to the world. He hence decides to recruit Schemer, a contract killer to have Dhruv eliminated. Schemer studies Dhruv in depth and comes up with a devious plan to prove him a criminal in the eyes of law! Schemer draws the first blood when he entices Dhruv into a well laid trap. Schemer manages to falsely implicate him in the death of a by stander who was actually murdered using Dhruv's star blade. The police views this incident as a mere accident and Dhruv is set out on bail. Schemer is unperturbed as he has more aces up his sleeve! Dhruv has become a proclaimed offender according to the law of the land! Will Schemer succeed in his assignment! Natasha is on the look out for the people behind this conspiracy. But can she reach out to Dhruv in time? Watch a master planner and master fighter battle it out exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Saja E Maut(Death Sentence)

description: India is all set to take a big leap into the world of space and technology by launching a space service station! This would serve as a maintenance depot to the numerous satellites which are about to be decommissioned soon and thereby prolonging its life span! The space organization has developed a heavy duty laser specifically for this project. A dangerous criminal named Super Nova seeks this laser for his own ulterior motives. Dhruv has been selected for a secret space mission to Mars. He was training inside the space training station when Super Nova attacks the space station along with his goons to steal the laser! Dhruv had managed to tame the goons but was rendered helpless when super nova had the director for the space programs as hostage! Several guards lost their eyesight after they were exposed to bright ultraviolet light transmitted by Super Nova! Super Nova has been successful in blackmailing Prabhu Shrivastav, the man responsible for launch of satellites and has implanted a device in the satellite. Super Nova is a maniac who would stop at nothing to accomplish his dreams. What are his plans and what's the secret of the packet that has been sent to space? With Dhruv turning blind and betrayal of their cause by the scientists, the story is poised for an exciting finish exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Andhi Maut(Blind Death)

description: Couple of years ago a UFO had crashed on the Indian soil. The illiterate villagers taking it to be a bad omen migrated to a different place. The very site of the crash has been selected as the launching pad of the rocket to Mars, with Dhruv being the lone crew. Nostradamus has tricked the jail authorities to provide him with a computer in lieu of computerized forecast of their future. The unsuspecting guards provide him with gemstones to harness the energy of the solar planets and escape from the high security prison. Nostradamus had a gut feeling that something is amiss in the mars project and Dr. Saha, the man heading this mission is up to some mischief. He investigates the storage facilities and finds that some crucial components are missing. He alerts Dhruv about the malpractice. Dhruv decides to investigate the mission to Mars! Are Dr. Saha and Dr. Venkat Raju swindling money from the project? The final countdown has almost begun. Dhruv and Nostradamus are racing against time to obtain proof against Dr. Saha! But will they succeed in their endeavor? To add to the existing confusion two aliens who were hibernating under the earth decide to resurface. Take off your imagination exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Shadyantra(Conspiracy)
